name: SpongeBob SquarePants: Reef Rumble
summary: Bikini Bottom's greatest (and not-so-greatest) martial artists have gathered to determine ocean floor suprema-sea! Remember, no eye-gouging or tentacle biting...now let's rumble! What kind of game do you want to play? Arcade or tournament? Choose a fighter: SpongeBob, Patrick, Sandy, Squidward, Larry or Mr.Krabs.
